###  http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#CreateResource
:CreateResource rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                         <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Action> ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> """Introduce a new data record into a DPP module where no prior
         record exists for that resource identifier."""@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Create"@en .


###  http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#DelegateAccess
:DelegateAccess rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                         <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Action> ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> """Transfer a subset of one's own access rights to another
         Principal for a bounded scope and time period."""@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Delegate"@en .


###  http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#DeleteResource
:DeleteResource rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                         <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Action> ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> """Remove a DPP resource record, subject to data retention
         obligations."""@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Delete"@en .


###  http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#ReadResource
:ReadResource rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                       <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Action> ;
              <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> """Retrieve and inspect the content of a DPP resource without
         modifying it."""@en ;
              <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Read"@en .


###  http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#UpdateResource
