                         <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Action> ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Modify the content of an existing DPP resource record."@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Update"@en .


